Finance Minister Pravin Gordhan is in Parliament delivering the ministry&#8217;s medium-term budget policy statement.The mini-budget comes ahead of Standard and Poor s credit rating review in December. Rating agencies Fitch and Standard &amp; Poor s both have South Africa s credit outlook at BBB- with a negative outlook, one notch above junk status. Gordhan is also expected to announce National Treasury s views on growth prospects.Read Gordhan&#8217;s full speech below.